FIRSTLY, THANK you for downloading my map!

This map is the only map made with an double bridge! There is two secret rooms in the map, one for T and one for CT, good luck finding them ;-)

You are more than welcome to join us at: 217.163.30.167:27015 - [DK] Hoejhus 24/7 |FFA - 100 TICK!|

You can also just join our SteamGroup: http://steamcommunity.com/groups/HoejhusServer

I hope you will Enjoy the map and I hope to see you soon on the server! ;-)

NB! NB! NB!
I decide to delete the Disco in this Version because it takes ALOT of time for people downloading the map, if its NOT a "Fast Download" server. But if your server is running Fast download, I really recommend my version with an disco, download it here! - http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/86779

You can still download my DoubleMix_v1 WITH Disco - Here: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/86779
